<template>

</template>

<script>
import {provide, ref} from "vue";

export default {
  name: "Staus_panel",
  setup() {
    let required_fields = ref({
      "Broker": "broker.connected",
      "Raspi": "//",
      "M1": "fcu.bridge_motor.motor_1_current",
      "M2": "fcu.bridge_motor.motor_2_current",
      "Main": "main_position_motor.txpdo_1.statusword",
      "Back": "back_position_motor.txpdo_1.statusword",
      "Lat": "lat_position_motor.txpdo_1.statusword",
      "FCU": "fcu.status_01.general_status",
      "IMU": "imu.status_01.general_status",
      "Battery": "battery.pack_info.current",
      "High Pow": "battery.pack_info.status",
      "Palpeur": "fcu.height_sensor.height_sensor_status",
      "Cockpit": "cockpit_arduino.pilot_command_01.speedcommand",
    })

    provide("home_sts_panel_fields")

    return {required_fields}
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
